# Coral Kingdoms reef (locked)

**Do not change the Coral Kingdoms reef** (colony count, spacing, size multiplier, procedural shapes, palette, bed offset, or reef fish shadows) **unless the user explicitly asks** to modify the coral reef.

Coral Kingdoms is toggled via `setCoralReefEnabled(true)` when `location.name === 'Coral Kingdoms'`. Call it **before** `setWaterBodyType` (see `coral-kingdoms-water.mdc`).

